# Technical Stack (Backend Focused)
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Core Backend
- **Language**: Java 17 LTS
- **Framework**: Spring Boot 3.4+
- **Build Tool**: Gradle (Groovy DSL)
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA (Hibernate 6.x), QueryDSL 5.x

## Database & Storage
- **RDBMS**: MySQL 9.x (InnoDB, utf8mb4)
- **Cache/Session**: Redis (Lettuce Client)
- **Messaging**: Apache Kafka (Event-Driven Architecture)

## Architecture Components
- **API Pattern**: RESTful API (OpenAPI 3.x), gRPC (Internal, Future)
- **Security**: Spring Security 6.x, OAuth2/OIDC (Google, Kakao)
- **Logging/Monitoring**: SLF4J, Logback, Micrometer

## External Services Integration
- **AI/ML**: OpenAI API (via RestClient), LangChain (Python Service Integration)
- **Devices**: Vendor OAuth2 APIs (Samsung Health, etc.)

